<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2006] Documentation of hbase-site.xml parameters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2006</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is nowhere on the site or wiki a detailed examination of the parameters behind HBase. You have to open hbase-default.xml to see them and their descriptions. A page on the wiki with descriptions would be nice&lt;/p&gt;</description>
